snippet.title: These Timeless Charlie Chaplin Quotes Are Life Changing | Worth Listening To!
snippet.description:
These Timeless Charlie Chaplin Quotes Are Life Changing. Worth Listening To! 

Sir Charles Spencer Chaplin Jr. KBE was an English comic actor, filmmaker, and composer who rose to fame in the era of silent film. He became a worldwide icon through his screen persona, the Tramp, and is considered one of the film industry's most important figures.

These are vivid sayings and quotes from Charlie Chaplin. The best quotes and aphorisms of Charlie Chaplin that will make you think about many things in life. Life quotes from Charlie Chaplin are definitely worth your time.

Thank you for watching!
